{"tid":1555599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方透過醫管局取得「爆眼少女」醫療報告","createTime":"2019-09-09T11:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T12:00:42.000Z","uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5eb14269ef29e75342e86618c2135cad49ece79","tid":1555599,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"早前在811衝突中，一名少女懷疑被警方以布袋彈射中右眼。警方證實，已經根據《警察通例》第50章(7)條，向法庭申請手令，並已透過醫管局取得事主的醫療報告，警方正審視相關的資料。<br />\n<br />\n警方解釋，根據通例，如果相關資料有助警方偵查罪案，可以向法庭宣誓並申請手令，由於警方與法庭的申請過程是在宣誓下進行，因此不能在記者會上透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n警方又說，當日在尖沙咀一帶，有人縱火，警方亦在當日拘捕30多人，部分人被暫控暴動罪，因此法庭向警方批出手令，讓警方取得當日的資料。"},{"pid":"a55db7c7c8760b99b6a153fa03b109ffd4300adc","tid":1555599,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">義務心理諮詢與情緒支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546984</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人頌經? 南無大願地藏王菩薩</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b74181ed83e654a6f0c2d96daba239efb2816e91","tid":1555599,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cc253969484c369bda23d451a24ebc28578091","tid":1555599,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"faa6c4f829cf9fcdada9bbde2bd8cd35087e21d4","tid":1555599,"uid":264299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地話唔想俾狗啊"},{"pid":"4d5fa9ab578af7c5ba6268dc73e6a1db0bcb431c","tid":1555599,"uid":46388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65670c0fb3395098612959bfb5d9de075aecc476","tid":1555599,"uid":82703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 醫管局出賣病人資料 <br />\n咁搞法根本無私隱可言"},{"pid":"5ac35521c1ddf85914d84ba4fe73013020a21b79","tid":1555599,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c06bcc8ee09d48f18ec792902be8e8fedc776dd","tid":1555599,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"你夠膽告爆眼女暴動<br />\n<br />\n後果自負"},{"pid":"8e88098f740cc6c0135d3306002c0f8a2f579149","tid":1555599,"uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"雖然可恨，但唔可以咁講醫院出賣病人私隱，如果佢做足程序向法庭申請，有手令醫院無可能唔俾。"},{"pid":"c63691d33c3aa2f4f7aa3f41210c6cab7d95f9ee","tid":1555599,"uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"所以我地應該要多啲諗下，用法律途徑去整治啲狗，但礙於示威者認為自己違法在先，驚俾人反告，可能要等一日真係有人肯犧牲自己同警隊攬炒先可能帶得起頭去團結做班警犬"}]}